Personal Injury.5018e46d-28d0-477c-ab6f-f43ce11f65ba: {"qTopic":"Personal Injury","date":"09-12-19","question":"Legal time limit to sue for personal injury in Korea","questionDetails":"Accident happened in 2015, after years of medical tribulations I am still injured and in pain (spinal injury, had to undergo surgery too).
